{"tid":896877,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有中國旅行社擬組團到小西灣參觀街市　網民：隨時食個tea飲個茶都冇位","createTime":"2018-11-10T12:12:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-10T13:11:14.000Z","uid":39464,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9783b30d271f83e17fd041d9bc697feac180114a","tid":896877,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T12:12:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181110/s00001/e3ae3845e84f718fbea10b447f361059.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181110%2Fs00001%2Fe3ae3845e84f718fbea10b447f361059.jpg&h=1871ece1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港珠澳大橋通車後，不少內地旅行社都帶團經大橋來港，除了在東涌一帶逗留，部分旅行團亦會入市區。有網民發現，有內地旅行社近日擬組團來港，除了參觀港珠澳大橋，還會到小西灣參觀街市。<br />\n<br />\n本報在杭州「華運國旅」的網站及微信均找到相關旅行團，該公司自稱是「中老年旅遊專業服務商」，近日推出「廣深珠、香港、澳門、桂林、陽朔、韶山經典11日空調旅遊專列」，團費2380元人民幣，11月16日和12月10日均有團出發。<br />\n<br />\n根據旅行社網站，該團會帶團友暢遊8大名城，感受一國兩制，團友在上海、南京和杭州等火車站都可以上旅行團專用火車隨團南下，第3日就會來到香港，參觀維港和淺水灣等地。到第4日，旅行團就會參觀小西灣的本灣市場，「了解香港本地普通民眾的生活，別有一番風味」。參觀完小西灣街市後，團隊就會乘車經過港珠澳大橋，「感受大橋的雄偉」，到珠海後就會繼續內地的行程。<br />\n<br />\n該團的資料昨日一度被轉載至facebook群組「柴灣人柴灣事」，有網民留言，不滿旅行團參觀街市，質疑小西灣難以容納那麼多人和旅遊巴，擔心「隨時食個tea飲個茶都冇位」。<br />\n<br />\n本灣市場是領展旗下街市，該街市整體承租商建華集團回覆本報表示，絕無聯絡或接洽任何旅行團參觀街市，強調會致力提升街市的服務質素，為街坊提供便利舒適的購物環境。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181110/s00001/e3be09e6938d2449ac04de2040a04a61.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181110%2Fs00001%2Fe3be09e6938d2449ac04de2040a04a61.jpg&h=31cfebd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181110/s00001/e3d5ebb8c50e3c11556a38a6f59016e1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181110%2Fs00001%2Fe3d5ebb8c50e3c11556a38a6f59016e1.png&h=80a164da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181110/s00001/e3db9b020bc7b3ad59af43ab4bde79e7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181110%2Fs00001%2Fe3db9b020bc7b3ad59af43ab4bde79e7.png&h=d08ec68c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181110/s00001/1541845452504\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181110%2Fs00001%2F1541845452504&d=u4lFlARRK0xS5ZTiuoZmRcP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=26144a61\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181110%2Fs00001%2F1541845452504&h=ac054111\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181110/s00001/1541845452504</a>"},{"pid":"835903cd0af0377d83c5d98e0f16fe9989bcb7d1","tid":896877,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T12:14:38.000Z","msg":"小西灣都無得避<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"777fc4da19b250636982720131a061f7f5e65eaa","tid":896877,"uid":29675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T12:16:57.000Z","msg":"東涌去小西灣參觀街市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f9087aff17db54667f391d44a0d690018e90c10","tid":896877,"uid":21917,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T12:17:36.000Z","msg":"原來電腦大爆炸個呀伯真係預言家黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c813ea2fba2eaf5de804c8cd6ceaab60bc1c30be","tid":896877,"uid":54264,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T12:20:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ghf9qbq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGhf9qbq.gif&h=d3440b69&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f3ffe547ebfbba70564685a50fe498c1bfde9bf","tid":896877,"uid":38194,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T12:21:08.000Z","msg":"小西灣 RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj